Author: Falkgornos
Title: [ANN][ICO] DAFZO.IO - A Decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform

And also Dafzo are developing ASSP system that will protect date too.

Body: Dafzo ecosystem builds on Blockchain and it can help the logistics industry in the following manner. 1.With the implementation of Blockchain, Blockchain will avoid the additional delay due to improper documentation and dependability on each another. 2. Blockchain will enable to collect and analyze the data at every step-in order to make the process much effective next time. 3. Blockchain will help in creating and increasing the level of transparency resulting in the reduction of TAT. 4. Automation of logistics on ports helping to prevent the malicious manipulation of data. 5. Increased consumer security and trust. 6. Shared Assets, Infrastructure, and Talent. 7. Reduction in overall TAT.

Author: prateeks885
Title: [ANN][ICO] DAFZO.IO - A Decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform
Body: The logistics industry is one of the most unorganized industry. Blockchain will help the logistics industry in its revival. Blockchain can help the logistics industry in the following ways;   1.With the implementation of Blockchain, Blockchain will avoid the additional delay due to improper documentation and dependability on each another. 2. Blockchain will enable to collect and analyze the data at every step in order to make the process much effective next time. 3. Blockchain will help in creating and increasing the level of transparency resulting in the reduction of TAT. 4. Automation of logistics on ports helping to prevent the malicious manipulation of data. 5. Increased consumer security and trust. 6. Shared Assets, Infrastructure, and Talent. 7. Reduction in overall TAT.

Body: The blockchain is the future of logistics. And there are several reasons for this: - Blockchain will help to maintain the data in a proper and effective manner. - With the implementation of Blockchain, Blockchain will avoid the additional delay due to improper documentations and dependability on each another. - Blockchain will help in creating and increasing the level of transparency resulting in the reduction of TAT. - Automation of logistics on ports helping to prevent the malicious manipulation of data. - Increased consumer security and trust. Author: Neilobit
Title: [ANN][ICO] DAFZO.IO - A Decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform
Body: Website- https://dafzo.io    Pre White Paper   Twitter  Facebook   Telegram   Medium   YouTube         Dafzo: Weltweit erste dezentrale globale P2P-Logistikplattform    Dafzofreut sich zu verkünden DFZ, der Token zur Revolutionierung der Logistikbranche.    DFZwird durch einen Token-Verkauf verfügbar sein, der für die Gemeinschaft geöffnet ist.      DFZ Token Pre ICO startet am 29. März 2018 01:00 UTC Ende 30. April 2018 2359 UTC  Das öffentliche Angebot beginnt am 1. Juni 2018 01:00 UTC Ende 30 Juni 2018 2359 UTC    Einführung in Dafzo    Dafzo is the World's first decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform which is about the disrupt the USD 8,797 billion logistics industry with its Patent International Trade Finance technology.         Dafzo:  Konzeptioneller Beweiß    Dafzo has launched its Beta Product in India in name of Courierhome which is India's first online courier aggregator using AI and is the biggest reverse logistics platform in India having tie-ups with the logistics giants such as FedEx and Aramex offering domestic as well as international shipping.        Besuchen Sie Dafzos offizielle ICO Crowdsale Website    Probleme in der Logistik Industrie      Die Logistikindustrie handhabt einen Datenhaufen, der zur Zeit in der altmodischen , zentralisierten Weise gehandhabt wird und einen unangemessenen Personalaufwand erfordert. Logistics Industry ist an verschiedenen Standorten tätig, d. H. In unterschiedlichen Jurisdiktionen. Die Handhabung einer einzigen Lieferkette für ein einzelnes Produkt könnte für einen Anfänger einen Alptraum darstellen und sogar für einen erfahrenen Logistikexperten einen ernsthaften Stammschmerz bedeuten.  Aufgrund eines zentralisierten Systems ist es für Logistikunternehmen nicht möglich, jede Bewegung ihrer Transportmittel zu erfassen und gleichzeitig mit dem Empfänger zu kommunizieren. Aufgrund dieser Lücke Empfänger oft slip Fenster Zeit für seine Lieferung, die Unannehmlichkeiten verursacht, Lieferverzögerung und zusätzliche Kosten für Logistikunternehmen für die erneute Lieferung der Sendung . Noch heute kämpfen Logistikunternehmen mit innovativen Methoden für Expresszustellung und 24x7 Support für Abholung und Ablegen.    Zuletzt Aber am wichtigsten , derzeit Internationale Verkäufe Import und Exporterfolgen in der traditionellen Methode Import und Export werden in traditioneller Methode über das zentralisierte Banksystem durchgeführt . Das beinhaltet eine [substantielle hohe] Gebühr, eine komplexe Methode, um Frachtbriefe und Akkreditive zu bearbeiten, andere Papiere, die zu Zahlungsverzug und Warenbesitz führen.    Lösung     Dafzo ist eine Lösung für alle diese Probleme im Zusammenhang mit internationalen Versand und lokale Lieferung. Dafzo arbeitet auf einer einzigen Plattform zusammen, um Daten zu teilen und Ressourcen zu optimieren, von denen alle profitieren, also Nutzer und Partner. Das dezentrale Logistiksystem Dafzo P2P bietet:   a). Patent International Trade Finance Technologie " System, das für vollautomatische International Trade Finance Clearing-System steht. b). Dezentrales Logistik-Aggregator-Ökosystem mit grenzenlosem E-Commerce-Marktplatz zu einem niedrigen Preis. c). 24x7 innerhalb der Stadt Express-Lieferungsystem d). Globale P2P-Depotbank & Partnerprogramme e). Beitrag Liquidität und Nutzen. Author: rescue_96
Title: [ANN][ICO] DAFZO.IO - A Decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform
Body: Website- https://dafzo.io    Pre White Paper   Twitter  Facebook   Telegram   Medium   YouTube      https://image.prntscr.com/image/zS6k5_nCTwyW9heHkNCN8A.png   Dafzo:  World's first decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform    Dafzo is pleased to annouce DFZ, the token to revolutionize the logistics industry.    DFZ will be available through a token sale open to the community.        DFZ Token Pre ICO will start on 29th March 2018 01:00 UTC  END 30 April 2018 2359 UTC  Public offering will start on 1 of June 2018 01:00 UTC END 30 of June 2018 2359 UTC    Introduction to Dafzo    Dafzo is the World's first decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform which is about the disrupt the USD 8,797 billion logistics industry with its Patent International Trade Finance technology.         Dafzo:  Proof of Concept    Dafzo has launched its Beta Product in India in name of Courierhome which is India's first online courier aggregator using AI and is the biggest reverse logistics platform in India having tie-ups with the logistics giants such as FedEx and Aramex offering domestic as well as international shipping.        Visit Dafzo's offical ICO Crowdsale website    Problem in Logistics Industry      Logistics Industry handles a pile of data and that is currently handled in the old-fashioned, centralized way, and requires unreasonable staff overage. Logistics Industry operates in different locations i.e. different jurisdictions, handling a single supply chain for a single product could pose a nightmare for a beginner, and a serious pain in the stem for even a seasoned logistics expert.  Due to a centralized system, it’s not possible for logistics companies to track record of every movement of their transportation and connect with the receiver at the same time for delivery. Due to this gap receiver often slip window time for its delivery that causes inconvenience, delay of delivery and additional cost to logistics companies for re-delivery of the consignment. Even today logistics companies are struggling with innovate methods for express delivery and 24 x7 support for pick up and drop.    Last But most important, currently International sales i.e. import and export are done in the traditional method import and export are done in traditional method via the centralized banking system.That involves a substantial high fee, a complex method of handling Bills of lading & Letter of credit, other paperwork resulting in delay payment and possession of goods.    Solution      Dafzo is a solution to all such problems related to International shipping and local delivery. Dafzo collaborates on a single platform to share data and optimize resources for the benefit of everyone i.e. user and partners. Dafzo P2P decentralized logistics system offers:   a). Patent International Trade Finance technology” system which stands for fully automated International Trade Finance Clearing system. b). Decentralized logistics aggregator ecosystem with borderless e-commerce marketplace at a low price. c). 24x7 within city Express delivery  system d). Global P2P custodian & partner  programme e). contribution liquidity & benefits. Author: tiCeR
Title: [ANN][ICO] DAFZO.IO - A Decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform
Body: Ok but that process to get the patent through could take years and years or am I mistaken here? That's how I know it, but maybe it's different for you for whatever reason.

Author: rescue_96
Title: [ANN][ICO] DAFZO.IO - A Decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform
Body: @tiCeR Yes, you are right about the patent process, However Our legal team has filed UK patent National application & international application with EUIPO on January  2018 and same time our legal team have submitted  PDAS with WIPO for first priority claim.  As per PDAS first filing priority  claim is in favor of Dafzo against any other inventor from PCT countries. We have submitted  fast track examination with applicable jurisdiction and expected to receive patent within 18 months to 24 months time-frame.   @Nischal Arvind S Our Legal Advisor : https://www.linkedin.com/in/nischal-arvind-s-a026291a  Our official partners : https://www.nassandguild.com

Author: tiCeR
Title: [ANN][ICO] DAFZO.IO - A Decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform
Body: Thanks for the honest reply. Will study your whitepaper and have a deeper look at your project. Having a patent in place would actually be awesome but now you have to be patient anyway

Body: Hey there . I just find out about this project. I make a quick research of your website. I want to know who is behind your team and what are you experience you have .

Author: rescue_96
Title: [ANN][ICO] DAFZO.IO - A Decentralized Global P2P Logistics Platform
Body: @phonglouis I did mention earlier that our team page is getting updated as we are adding more and more people into the project.  I am also advisor to the board, for crypto currency and Ether Smart contract.  You will soon get the complete information about me and the team on the dafzo website.  Why Delay?  This project is very big and we are trying pool people from around the globe, And I would also like to point out All our partnership approaches  have given us positive response.
